Insider Activity


Individual




Thomas Boone Pickens



Mr. Thomas B. Pickens, III, is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Astrotech Corp., President at Beta Computer Systems, Inc., Chairman at 1st Detect Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Astrogenetix, Inc., Managing Partner at Sumpter Partners LP and Managing Partner at Tactic Advisors, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Trenwick America Corp. Mr. Pickens was previously employed as Chairman by US Utilities, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Catalyst Energy Corp., President by T.B. Pickens & Co., Inc., Chairman by Astrotech Space Operations LLC, President by Century Power Corp., President by Eury Dam Corp., President by Golden Bear Corp., General Partner by Grace Pickens Acquisition LP, President by Slate Creek Corp., Chairman by The Code Corp., Chairman by United Thermal Corp, and President by Vidilia Hydroelectric Corp. He also served on the board at Advocate, MD Financial Group, Inc. and Optifab, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Southern Methodist University.



